@GameStore.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5082

### Get all games list
GET {{['GameStore.Api_HostAddress']}}/games

### Get a single game by id
GET {{['GameStore.Api_HostAddress']}}/games/2562329e-d167-4f19-b1a0-48aff2bc65a7

